# Implementation Plan - Document Linking

## Goal Description
Ensure that when "Analysis Report" (分析表) or "Proof of Origin" (発生証明) files are attached to a lot (especially for Dump trucks), the actual filename is stored and displayed, rather than just a generic label.

## Proposed Changes

### Logic ([app.js](file:///c:/Users/tiesm/.gemini/antigravity/app.js))
#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///c:/Users/tiesm/.gemini/antigravity/app.js)
- **Submit Handler**:
    - For `attach-analysis-file`, if present, push `{ name: file.name, type: 'analysis', label: '分析表' }`.
    - For `attach-cert-file`, if present, push `{ name: file.name, type: 'proof', label: '証明書' }`.
    - (Keep existing truck docs logic but use filename there too).
- **Render Logic ([renderBatches](file:///c:/Users/tiesm/.gemini/antigravity/app.js#417-449))**:
    - Iterate through `batch.docs`.
    - Use the stored object to render the badge.
    - Title attribute: `doc.name` (The filename).
    - Display text or Icon: `doc.label` or specific icon.

